<p class="mt-6 border-l-2 border-eai-blueprint/40 pl-4 text-xs leading-relaxed text-eai-blueprint">
  Campus maps show intellectual and operating relationships among independent
  institutions sharing substrate, vocabulary, and editorial standards. They do
  not imply legal merger, financial consolidation, or operational control. The
  Library at schooltrusts.net, the Advocates for School Trust Lands coalition
  at schooltrustlands.net, the Oregon Advocates for School Trust Lands chapter,
  and the Oregon Websites and Watersheds Project (ORWW) are independent
  organizations. Each has its own board, its own staff or volunteer leadership,
  and its own editorial direction. The Eighth Anchor Institute hosts the campus
  and codifies the shared standards. It does not govern its allied buildings.
</p>
